---
import { siteConfig } from "../site.config";
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-brand-navy/10">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-10">
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div>
        <img src="/logo.svg" alt={siteConfig.brand} width="130" height="40" class="h-9 w-auto" />
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand-navy/70">
          Positionnement, ghostwriting et optimisation LinkedIn pour construire une autorité qui attire des opportunités.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-sm text-brand-navy/80">
        <div class="font-semibold text-brand-navy">Navigation</div>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li><a class="hover:text-brand-navy" href="/services">Services</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-brand-navy" href="/etudes-de-cas">Études de cas</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-brand-navy" href="/blog">Blog</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-brand-navy" href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="text-sm text-brand-navy/80">
        <div class="font-semibold text-brand-navy">Contact</div>
        <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <a
            class="rounded-full border border-brand-navy/15 px-4 py-2 font-semibold hover:bg-white/40"
            href={siteConfig.cta.whatsappUrl}
          >
            Écrire sur WhatsApp
          </a>
          <a
            class="rounded-full bg-brand-blue px-4 py-2 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-brand-navy"
            href={siteConfig.cta.callUrl}
          >
            Réserver un appel
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-2 border-t border-brand-navy/10 pt-6 text-xs text-brand-navy/60 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between">
      <div>© {year} {siteConfig.legalName}. Tous droits réservés.</div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a class="hover:text-brand-navy" href="/mentions-legales">Mentions légales</a>
        <a class="hover:text-brand-navy" href="/politique-de-confidentialite">Confidentialité</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

